race.description: Interstate Hotel Flinders Island Cup Plate (C6)
race.comment: SH'BOURNE MIDNIGHT (6) just missed here first-up over this distance seeking the hat-trick. Should tighten right up following that outing and is proven second up. Darmanin sticks aboard and he rates the one to beat. LOVIN' BEV (8) hits the race and peak fitness and is busting to win. She has been heavily bet all campaign and sits at the bottom of the handicap. A live chance. GARCON D'ESPOIR (7) resumes and has the numbers if he's presented forward. Will come into his own over further, but he has won fresh and has to be kept safe. ADACHI (3) is racing well and will enjoy a soft on-pace run. He'll be around the mark.
